{"tid":2488020,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"科興提供美洲盃疫苗 美斯都要打？","createTime":"2021-04-14T03:14:24.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-14T06:19:39.000Z","uid":282925,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"5e9568f4c48c1e5db7412675be9f589518f1bb1a","tid":2488020,"uid":282925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T03:14:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://sports.now.com/mobileweb/news/details?id=33025637415\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsports.now.com%2Fmobileweb%2Fnews%2Fdetails%3Fid%3D33025637415&d=t2%2FAN0mLur8%2Bj%2B1TvbkzvuNdVtVfIexd6qH9K0u6Sk4%3D&h=2d7b9802\" target=\"_blank\">https://sports.now.com/mobileweb/news/details?id=33025637415</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now Sports】今夏美洲國家盃賽會獲得科興提供5萬劑疫苗，予參賽球員接種。<br />\n南美洲足協會長阿里贊祖杜明基斯周二宣佈，獲科興疫苗捐贈5萬新冠疫苗，提供給今夏美洲國家盃的參賽球員。杜明基斯在聲明中說：「這是南美足球大家庭所得的最佳禮物。科興明白足球是我們最重要的比賽。」<br />\n<br />\n本屆美洲國家盃決賽周由阿根廷和哥倫比亞聯合主辦，6月13日開鑼，參賽的男足足球員都需要接種，整個接種工作在比賽舉行前完成；參賽球星包括鼎鼎大名的美斯、尼馬、蘇亞雷斯等人。<br />\n<br />\n杜明基斯在聲明中特別感謝烏拉圭總統波烏的幫忙，表揚他促成科興為南美足協提供疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : &copy;AFP"},{"pid":"1724c8a856d756cf2341c46c857ce19de864185d","tid":2488020,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T03:16:53.000Z","msg":"美斯係西班牙人"},{"pid":"bb42772cf1e0a178af80baf1083301a2d1187264","tid":2488020,"uid":158145,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1724c8a856d756cf2341c46c857ce19de864185d","tid":2488020,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T03:16:53.000Z","msg":"美斯係西班牙人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T03:19:24.000Z","msg":"C朗先係"},{"pid":"366f2e598d885289c1bf1779a691e8d9e6ba75a8","tid":2488020,"uid":3962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T03:33:58.000Z","msg":"屌你呀"},{"pid":"fb818bc5352b769261e740d7f4bebfca1a9b7d3f","tid":2488020,"uid":136797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T03:35:14.000Z","msg":"支持全球打科興<br />\n加速病毒變種"},{"pid":"49a484c3053df7cc062f8c830ea56578a4f